data.description: Welcome to your modern oasis! Spectacular 4 bedroom + den Southeast Tucson home with a private backyard! Spacious open floor plan with designer paint, tile flooring, plantation shutters and large built in shelving unit to display your personal collections. Beautifully upgraded gourmet kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, granite counters and an oversized center island w/breakfast bar. Master suite has a private exit and adjoining bath with dual sink vanity and private toilet room. Generous backyard is complete with a covered patio and decorative rock landscape. Don't miss this well cared for beauty! See this home today and make it yours!
